{"tid":1063033,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐聯劇本我已經諗好 利記奪冠","createTime":"2019-03-15T13:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T18:01:55.000Z","uid":1369,"like":47,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b6aedabbfc85b8f7a82b31231d481ae2bd3118dc","tid":1063033,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T13:00:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">八強</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利物浦5:0大炒波圖<br />\n<br />\n以破竹之勢在4強對上廢老美斯帶領既疤<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4強</span></span><br />\n<br />\n正牌美c對上埃及美c <br />\n首回合利物浦作客以1:0小勝<br />\n<br />\n次回合開賽不久 vvd因利迷瘋狂打飛機場地濕滑而跣腳 先失一球<br />\n<br />\n再被足球之神美c罰球絕殺 <br />\n<br />\n利物浦從此星散 跌落英冠<br />\n而廢中亦大受打擊 進入了精神病院<br />\n<br />\n在幾年過後 由謝拉特領隊帶領下 勇奪冠軍重返英超<br />\n<br />\n&lt;完&gt;"},{"pid":"4fddaea10edb7e44116e2e262eacbc5636059b30","tid":1063033,"uid":206337,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T14:20:48.000Z","msg":"然後決賽對戰曼城，比阿古路射入10球，完場10比0，奪得2019年歐聯冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c71ac9dd0b23df6e383afe8bc427c9bb49a97b","tid":1063033,"uid":72751,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T14:30:36.000Z","msg":"好撚老尷"},{"pid":"d85d52b50029aff8319a98cc6e03c7022eac3682","tid":1063033,"uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"波台所有朴初瓏都on99"},{"pid":"0d99aa3f07e6e8293b6cc254cb2920fa7d14b6dc","tid":1063033,"uid":54243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T14:51:36.000Z","msg":"8強疤俾我地曼雙殺喎<br />\n個剷本改下啦"},{"pid":"09395ccb46296566ad2839ee6a848a0bb6f9b370","tid":1063033,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:28:47.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"4b24fd07bb6cde3dcc596ba225a67a1e567d5e61","tid":1063033,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:56:42.000Z","msg":"係咪要